{"tid":1448760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IVE警察朋友爆料 有狗扮示威者","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:39:31.000Z","uid":183201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dfcdec4efe39c5f6180310a9d3e667924315fc89","tid":1448760,"uid":183201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"IVE警察朋友睇唔過眼<br />\n終於爆料由7月1日後已經派警察扮示威者<br />\n但係班前線一直唔知<br />\n之前掟汽油彈 掟磚頭的 大部分都係警察扮既<br />\n目的想增加社會對示威者既仇恨<br />\n令社會轉風向<br />\n<br />\n另外之前有部分示威者俾人捉都係警察扮<br />\n目的係想示威者滅聲唔敢再出黎<br />\n今日因爲係銅鑼灣俾示威者發現身分<br />\n所以唯有表明身分將佢地拘捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AQCZ3OY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAQCZ3OY.jpg&h=487eb10b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qO92g8Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqO92g8Z.jpg&h=2391cef0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}